# Two ways to wire Supabase:
#
# 1. Vercel ↔ Supabase integration (recommended for Vercel deploys).
#    Install the integration from the Vercel dashboard. It injects
#    SUPABASE_URL and SUPABASE_ANON_KEY into the project's env vars
#    automatically and the Vite build picks them up — no manual
#    config needed.
#
# 2. Standalone Supabase project, local dev, or any non-Vercel host:
#    copy this file to .env.local and fill in the values from your
#    Supabase project (Dashboard → Settings → API).

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT-REF.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=YOUR-ANON-PUBLIC-KEY

# Either prefix works — VITE_-prefixed wins if both are set:
# SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT-REF.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=YOUR-ANON-PUBLIC-KEY
